===Verb===
{{en-verb|ador|ing}}

# To [[worship]].
# To [[love]] with one's entire heart and soul; regard with deep [[respect]] and [[affection]].
#: ''It is obvious to everyone that Gerry absolutely '''adores''' Heather.''
